oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Baptism in West Fork Creek
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of a crowd of people of varying ages gathered for a baptism in West Fork Creek, near Mount Joy. Some are holding hands while standing in the water.

oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: People; Baptisms; Streams
